<div id="revolution_wrap" class="full">
  <div id="description" class="one_third">
    <h3>Japan Trip Overview</h3>
    <p>This app will help you, ONK, and trip volunteers keep the trip to Japan organized. You can use this site you
      manage your personal information,
      your letter of intent, and make payments to the trip.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="actions">
    <ul>
      <div class="box one_half">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="box_heading">
            <h4><a href="http://demo.t2themes.com/wordpress/advocate/feature/buy-stuff/">Setup Account</a></h4></div>
          <p>Create an account on the site and setup a password.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:10px;">Status:
            <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:green;">Complete</span></div>
          <%= link_to 'Update email or password', edit_user_registration_path %>.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="box one_half column_last">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="box_heading">
            <h4><a href="http://demo.t2themes.com/wordpress/advocate/feature/volunteer/">Registration Information</a>
            </h4></div>
          <p>In order to prepare for the trip we need address and contact information for students and parents. </p>
          <% if @registration == nil %>
              <div style="margin-top:10px;">Status:
                <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:red;">Incomplete</span></div>
              <%= link_to 'Fill out registration', registrations_edit_path %>
          <% else %>
              <div style="margin-top:10px;">Status:
                <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:green;">Complete</span></div>
              <%= link_to 'Edit your registration', registrations_edit_path %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="box one_half">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="box_heading">
            <h4><a href="http://demo.t2themes.com/wordpress/advocate/feature/donate/">Letter Of Intent</a></h4></div>
          <p>Your LOI curabitur blandit tempus porttitor. Duis mollis, est non commodo luctus..</p>
          <div style="margin-top:10px;">Status:
            <% if current_user.chaperone %>
                <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold;">Not Required</span>
            <% else %>
                <% if @registration == nil %>
                    <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold;color:red;">Complete Registration First</span>
                <% else %>
                    <% if @registration.file_ext != nil %>
                        <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:green;">Complete</span><br/>
                        <%= link_to 'Download LOI', "#{registrations_download_loi_path}/#{@registration.file_name}#{@registration.file_ext}" %><br/>
                    <% else %>
                        <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:red;">Incomplete</span><br/>
                    <% end %>
                    <%= form_tag registrations_upload_loi_path, multipart: true do %>
                        <input type="file" name="loi_file"/>
                        <input type="submit" value="Upload Letter of Intent" class="button black"/>
                    <% end %>
                <% end %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="box one_half column_last">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="box_heading">
            <h4><a href="http://demo.t2themes.com/wordpress/advocate/feature/share/">Payments</a></h4></div>
          <p>Every month you have a portion of your payment due for your trip.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:10px;">Status:
            <% if @registration == nil %>
                <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold;color:red;">Complete Registration First</span>
            <% else %>
                <span style="margin-left:20px;font-weight:bold; color:green;">Up to Date</span></div>
                <%= link_to 'View payment history' %>
            <% end %>
            </div>
      </div>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>